        <h2>How to Apply</h2>

        <p>Special Connections Academy offers a twelve-month program for our students, following the 10-month Broward County school calendar and a summer program.</p>

        <p>SPC has a rolling enrollment policy. If your child is eligible and there is availability, he/she can start at SPC in just a couple of weeks.</p>

        <h4>Schedule a Tour</h4>
        <p>We encourage you to visit our school to learn more about our program and approach.</p>
